---
import { SITE } from '@content/site'
import SectionLabel from './ui/SectionLabel.astro'
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="bg-koneko-bg py-section-mobile lg:py-section-desktop"
  aria-labelledby="cta-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-koneko-primary/30 bg-koneko-card overflow-hidden p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 text-center">

      <!-- Fondo decorativo -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-koneko-primary/8 via-transparent to-koneko-neon/4 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-koneko-primary to-transparent"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <SectionLabel text="EMPIEZA HOY" />

        <h2
          id="cta-heading"
          class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-koneko-text mt-4 mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        >
          Descubre por qué tu negocio no está convirtiendo al máximo
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-koneko-text-muted mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Auditoría gratuita. Sin compromiso. Resultados en 24 horas.
        </p>

        <a
          href={SITE.ctaHref}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl bg-koneko-primary hover:bg-koneko-primary-light text-white font-semibold text-base transition-all duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-koneko-primary/30 hover:shadow-koneko-primary/50 hover:scale-[1.02]"
        >
          {SITE.ctaLabel}
        </a>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-koneko-text-muted">
          ¿Prefieres escribir directamente?
          <a
            href="mailto:info@konekoads.com"
            class="text-koneko-primary-light hover:text-koneko-text transition-colors underline underline-offset-2 ml-1"
          >
            info@konekoads.com
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
